Date 2007-4-15
Summary: xlslib release 0.2.5 (ALPHA)
-----------------------------------------------------------
This is an alpha release of xlslib.
It includes:

- library source changes so it will compile
- configure script rebuilt
- test application now compiles and runs
- Various other improvements
- Its quite likely that the sister PHP library is broken,
  if anyone wants to help to get it operational, please 
  contact the administrators.
- A "C" interface is in the works - stay tuned.

Date 2008-02-09
Summary: xlslib release 1.0.0
-----------------------------------------------------------
- 32/64 bit buildable
- make clean works better
- A "C" interface - see xlslib.h for interface

Date 2008-10-1
Summary: xlslib release 1.2.0
-----------------------------------------------------------
- Updated to create BIFF8 formatted files (from BIFF5) for:
- full 256 columns x 64000 rows!
- support for ASCII and UNICODE strings in labels and sheet names
- compliance with mandatory items specified in OpenOffice.org's Excel Spec

Date 2009-6-20
Summary: xlslib release 1.5.0
-----------------------------------------------------------
- Significant bug fixes and performance improvements
- Possible now to create "Properties" objects

